(265, '_transient_auxin_phlox__remote_changelog', '<h4 class=\"aux-changelog-item-title\"><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-version\">Version <strong>2.3.0</strong></span><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-date\">(19.11.2018)</span></h4><ul><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> 29 New typography options added to theme options.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> Introducing Templates Kit Library.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Major under the hood improvements to demo importer.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Improvements in Advanced Image Element for Elementor.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Improvement for position of burger menu on mobile size.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Improvement in retrieving and displaying the list of demos applied.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> Now you can uninstall a demo content after importing the content.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> New top header options added to page options.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> Adding Extra pulse animations to entrance animations.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> Adding quick view option for recent product element.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> Adding an option to change the text of subtotal in shop cart.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> Adding new header layout, \"Wish list\" and \"My account\" buttons to header.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> Adding background hover options for Info Box Element.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> New preload options added to advanced image element, plus, adding max width and height options.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Fixing an issue with lightbox features in image element.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> An issue with WooCommerce Ajax notification style in homepage fixed.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Style fix for top header when sticky footer is enabled.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> Adding new preset layout for top header bar with secondary message.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-pro\">Pro</span> New SVG Element added for Elementor page builder.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-pro\">Pro</span> Shape Element added for Elementor page builder.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Fixing an issue for displaying the search icon on header.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Some incompatibility issues in go pricing plugin fixed.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Improvement in \"on sale\" badge styles on advanced recent product.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Close the burger or overlay menu after clicking on a relative menu link.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Improving the style of Dropdown element.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Improvement in Info Box Element.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-new\">New</span> New options for WooCommerce cart in header added.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Fixing style issues for star rating component.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Fixing styles of footer meta in single news page.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Fixing an issue with the featured image in Elementor posts.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Fixing some undefined variables.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Some issues on FAQ Element fixed.</li></ul><h4 class=\"aux-changelog-item-title\"><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-version\">Version <strong>2.2.24</strong></span><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-date\">(02.09.2018)</span></h4><ul><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> An issue with redirect script fixed\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> An issue with light skin in burger menu fixed.</li></ul><h4 class=\"aux-changelog-item-title\"><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-version\">Version <strong>2.2.20</strong></span><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-date\">(21.08.2018)</span></h4><ul><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-improvement\">Improve</span> Improvement in entrance animations.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Invalid css value fixed in rtl.css\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> An issue with Elementor templates fixed.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> An issue with Elementor grid fixed.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Minor bugs fixed.</li></ul><h4 class=\"aux-changelog-item-title\"><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-version\">Version <strong>2.2.18</strong></span><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-date\">(10.08.2018)</span></h4><ul><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> An issue with scrollTo a section fixed.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> An issue with the vertical menu in responsive view fixed.</li></ul><h4 class=\"aux-changelog-item-title\"><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-version\">Version <strong>2.2.16</strong></span><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-date\">(05.08.2018)</span></h4><ul><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> An issue with page progress animations and ajax links fixed.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-fix\">Fix</span> Minor bugs fixed.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-pro\">Pro</span> Adding special Entrance Animation options to all Elementor Elements in Phlox Pro.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-pro\">Pro</span> Master Slider Pro updated to 3.2.7.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-pro\">Pro</span> Revolution Slider added to list of bundled plugins.\r</li><li><span class=\"aux-changelog-item-type aux-changelog-type-pro\">Pro</span> Layer Slider added to list of bundled plugins.</li></ul>', 'no'),
